dministrator will be within 15 minutes of an alert or emergency declaration by the customer response back to the customer will be within 30 minutes of receipt of the alert by the administrator standard development and test database support is provided monday friday 8 am 5 pm for assistance please submit a helpsu request tickets are assigned and responded to per sla escalation guidelines oracle requests mssql requests rates the database administration service is available by subscription and is charged monthly to your department's it services bill see the computing services rates page getting started to order the database administration service use orderit or submit a helpsu request under the request category billable services and the request type database administration services last modified fri 18 nov 2011 at 17 29 pages about this service overview maintenance activities monitoring roles and responsibilities business documents for database administration actions orderit find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages secure computing for technical professionals linux system administration mysql database hosting windows system administration footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
